gth `n` as `x`. If there is no such `n`, then use `0` by convention. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Topology/MetricSpace/PiNat.html#PiNat.shortestPrefixDiff","kind":"def","line":474,"name":"PiNat.shortestPrefixDiff","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Topology/MetricSpace/PiNat.lean#L474-L478"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/MetricSpace/PiNat.html#PiNat.exists_disjoint_cylinder\"><span class=\"name\">PiNat</span>.<span class=\"name\">exists_disjoint_cylinder</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>) → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">E</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>), <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Order.html#DiscreteTopology\">DiscreteTopology</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">E</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">((<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>) → <span class=\"fn\">