/a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Topology/MetricSpace/PiNat.html#PiNat.cylinder_eq_pi","kind":"theorem","line":115,"name":"PiNat.cylinder_eq_pi","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Topology/MetricSpace/PiNat.lean#L115-L118"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/MetricSpace/PiNat.html#PiNat.cylinder\"><span class=\"name\">PiNat</span>.<span class=\"name\">cylinder</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>) → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">E</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">((<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>) → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">E</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"In a product space `Π n, E n`, the cylinder set of length `n` around `x`, denoted\n`cylinder x n`, is the set of sequences `y` that coincide with `x` on the first `n` symbols, i.e.,\nsuch that `y i = x i` for all `i < n`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Topology/MetricSpace/PiNat.html#PiNat.cylinder","kind":"def","line":108,"name":"PiNat.cylinder","sourceLink":"https://gith